.claude/projects/

# Raw experiment data artifacts of the distill/ablation program are NOT committed — they live
# in the Notion experiments area (Research page) with a SHA-256 manifest. Analysis prose (.md)
# stays in git, as do small result JSONs elsewhere under research/ (e.g. trace_scaling_results).
.agents/docs/research/distill/*.json
.agents/docs/research/distill/*.jsonl
.agents/docs/research/distill/*.html
